Have this folder be parallel to /employers

In here will be the template files just like for example:
company.php
<?php
  $GLOBALS['dirpre'] = '';
  require_once($GLOBALS['dirpre'].'includes/header.php');
  $CCompany->view();
  require_once($GLOBALS['dirpre'].'includes/footer.php');
?>

But, the $GLOBALS['dirpre'] should be set to '../employers'